(17, '93.MMM a bežecký klub Furča', 'ZB-k', NULL, '<p>A&nbsp;za t&yacute;ždeň je to tu znova. Že čo? No predsa sviatok bežcov-marat&oacute;ncov. Medzin&aacute;rodn&yacute; marat&oacute;n mieru.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tak ako po minul&eacute; roky, aj tento, by ste n&aacute;s, &scaron;tartuj&uacute;cich pod hlavičkou O5 BK Furča , mali vidieť medzi pretek&aacute;rmi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>S&nbsp;č&iacute;slom 1185 vzdialenosť 42195 metrov pok&uacute;si sa&nbsp;pokoriť Juraj Fotul, za dva mesiace čerstv&yacute; sedemdesiatnik, člen čerstvo založen&eacute;ho Diamantov&eacute;ho klubu. A&nbsp;o tom, že mu to už dlho beh&aacute;, hovor&iacute; aj jeho 38 &scaron;tart na t&yacute;chto pretekoch.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>S&nbsp;najvy&scaron;&scaron;&iacute;m &scaron;tartov&yacute;m č&iacute;slom v&nbsp;marat&oacute;ne medzi mužmi, 1463, postav&iacute; sa&nbsp;už po 34 kr&aacute;t na &scaron;tart J&aacute;n Mičko, taktiež člen Diamantov&eacute;ho klubu. K&nbsp;jeho &scaron;tartom je nutn&eacute; podotkn&uacute;ť, že koľkokr&aacute;t st&aacute;l na &scaron;tarte, toľkokr&aacute;t aj dobehol do cieľa, ani raz nevzdal.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tret&iacute;m z na&scaron;ich pretek&aacute;rov, ktor&eacute;ho usporiadatelia MMM zaradili za jeho 27 doteraj&scaron;&iacute;ch &scaron;tartov v&nbsp;marat&oacute;ne na MMM do Diamantov&eacute;ho klubu, je Imrich Mih&oacute;k. M&ocirc;žete ho vidieť na trati s&nbsp;č&iacute;slom 1352 ako vodiča marat&oacute;ncov na v&yacute;sledn&yacute; čas 4:30:00.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Medzi ženami na najdlh&scaron;iu olympijsk&uacute; discipl&iacute;nu postavia sa&nbsp;a&nbsp;na&scaron;e farby bud&uacute; h&aacute;jiť Zuzana Bradovkov&aacute; a&nbsp;Andrea Repkov&aacute;. Zuzana Bradovkov&aacute; s&nbsp;č&iacute;slom 8223 bude po tret&iacute; kr&aacute;t &scaron;tartovať v&nbsp;tejto discipl&iacute;ne na MMM, Andrea Repkov&aacute; s&nbsp;č&iacute;slom 8085. Tiež to bude jej tret&iacute; &scaron;tart, podar&iacute; sa ako predo&scaron;l&eacute; dva pod 4 hodiny?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>A&nbsp;pre &uacute;plnosť, tu je prehľad v&scaron;etk&yacute;ch pretek&aacute;rov, &scaron;tartuj&uacute;cich pod hlavičkou O5 BK Furča-Ko&scaron;ice zoraden&yacute;ch podľa &scaron;tartov&eacute;ho č&iacute;sla.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Marat&oacute;n:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="width:302px">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td colspan="2" style="height:20px; width:47px">\r\n			<p>168</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td colspan="3" style="height:20px; width:108px">\r\n			<p>Benedik</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td colspan="2" style="height:20px; width:64px">\r\n			<p>Peter</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td colspan="2" style="height:20px; width:64px">\r\n			<p>1973</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td colspan="2" style="height:20px; width:47px">\r\n			<p>293</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td colspan="3" style="height:20px; width:108px">\r\n			<p>Mady</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td colspan="2" style="height:20px; width:64px">\r\n			<p>Tomas</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td colspan="2" style="height:20px; width:64px">\r\n			<p>1975</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td colspan="2" style="height:20px; width:47px">\r\n			<p>306</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td colspan="3" style="height:20px; width:108px">\r\n			<p>Hric</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td colspan="2" style="height:20px; width:64px">\r\n			<p>Miroslav</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td colspan="2" style="height:20px; width:64px">\r\n			<p>1977</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		